public class RawStateException
extends javax.telephony.InvalidStateException

Proxy for an InvalidStateException that holds enough information to determine the object whose state is not correct. This may be morphed at the Generic JTAPI layer into an InvalidStateExcedption and this thrown back to the calling application. Creation date: (2000-02-09 10:45:24)
